🤖 **Common preferences mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Blocking on main | Use DataStore with Flow |
| Blocking reads | Use Flow |
| No error handling | Handle errors |
| No type safety | Use typed keys |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use DataStore
val dataStore = context.dataStore

// 2. Use Flow for reads
dataStore.data.map { it[key] }.collect { value ->
    // Update UI
}

// 3. Handle errors
try {
    dataStore.edit { it[key] = value }
} catch (e: Exception) {
    // Handle error
}

// 4. Use typed keys
